typescript-eslint/parser',\n  plugins: ['@typescript-eslint'],\n  extends: ['eslint:recommended', 'plugin:@typescript-eslint/recommended'],\n  parserOptions: {\n    ecmaVersion: 2022,\n    sourceType: 'module',\n  },\n  rules: {\n    '@typescript-eslint/no-unused-vars': ['error', { argsIgnorePattern: '^_' }],\n  },\n  env: {\n    node: true,\n    es2022: true,\n  },\n};\n```\n\n---\n\n### 4. ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES\n\n**File:** `/workspace/.env`\n```\nDB_HOST=localhost\nDB_PORT=5432\nDB_USER=admin\nDB_PASSWORD=super_secret_password_123\nDB_NAME=monorepo_db\n```\n\n⚠️ **SECURITY ISSUE:** `.env` file contains plaintext credentials (DATABASE PASSWORD)\n\n---\n\n### 5. PACKAGES DETAILED BREAKDOWN\n\n---\n\n## PACKAGE: `@monorepo/core`\n\n**Location:** `/workspace/packages/core/`\n\n### package.json\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"@monorepo/core\",\n  \"version\": \"1.0.0\",\n  \"type\": \"module\",\n  \"main\": \"./dist/index.js\",\n  \"types\": \"./dist/index.d.ts\",\n  \"scripts\": {\n    \"build\": \"tsc\"\n  },\n  \"dependencies\": {\n    \"zod\": \"3.19.0\",\n    \"better-sqlite3\": \"^11.0.0\"\n  },\n  \"devDependencies\": {\n    \"@types/better-sqlite3\": \"^7.6.0\",\n    \"typescript\": \"^5.4.0\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### tsconfig.json\n```json\n{\n  \"compilerOptions\": {\n    \"target\": \"ES2022\",\n    \"module\": \"Node16\",\n    \"moduleResolution\": \"Node16\",\n    \"outDir\": \"./dist\",\n    \"rootDir\": \"./src\",\n    \"strict\": true,\n    \"composite\": true,\n    \"declaration\": true,\n    \"declarationMap\": true,\n    \"sourceMap\": true,\n    \"esModuleInterop\": true,\n    \"skipLibCheck\": true,\n    \"forceConsistentCasingInFileNames\": true\n  },\n  \"include\": [\"src/**/*.ts\"],\n  \"exclude\": [\"node_modules\", \"dist\", \"tests\"]\n}\n```\n\n### SOURCE FILES\n\n#### `/workspace/packages/core/src/index.ts` - Main Export Point\nExports all public types and functions from submodules.\n\n**Exports:**\n- Types: `User`, `CreateUserInput`, `UserFilters`